{"tid":913966,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"去年歐聯決賽藥檢肥佬？皇馬急為拉莫斯澄清","createTime":"2018-11-23T22:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T10:13:49.000Z","uid":30040,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e913344a0c0674a16da38c9f0de3bb2ab0564a","tid":913966,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T22:06:16.000Z","msg":"西甲豪門皇家馬德里周五突然急發聲明，為隊長沙治奧拉莫斯被指在2017年歐聯決賽後藥檢「肥佬」的報道澄清，並同時否認該名西班牙國腳在今年4月的一場西甲後，未有按慣常做法馬上接受藥檢的報道。<br />\n<br />\n德國《明鏡》周刊的報道指，沙治奧拉莫斯在2017年的歐聯決賽皇馬3:1擊敗祖雲達斯後進行的藥檢中，所呈交的樣本含有世界反禁藥組織（WADA）嚴禁使用物質dexamethasone的殘餘物，這是一種主治發炎的類固醇，但當局最後未有採取任何行動。皇馬周五所發的聲明強調，球隊當時在向有關當局遞交補充資料後，事情已經告一段落，又指《明鏡》周刊的報道「軟弱無力」。<br />\n《明鏡》周刊的報道亦有提到，沙治奧拉莫斯、皇馬和歐洲足協三方在去年的歐聯決賽後持續溝通，且一名只被名為「醫生A」的隊醫承認，自己在報告中忘記了填寫沙治奧拉莫斯曾經在比賽前注射兩劑dexamethasone，以抑制其肩膀和膝蓋的發炎。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，《明鏡》周刊報道，在今年4月皇馬對馬拉加的聯賽後，一名反禁藥官員曾經上報沙治奧拉莫斯未有按慣常做法，在比賽後馬上接受藥檢，堅持要先去洗澡，事件最後同樣不了了之。沙治奧拉莫斯的代表在傳媒聯絡嘗試得到回覆時，未有作出任何回應。"},{"pid":"990a3184eff867c0ddc6f47958aec0378b0474ed","tid":913966,"uid":30040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T22:11:47.000Z","msg":"呢份明鏡報就係之前解密左牙朗強姦案果份和解協議文件既報章<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n德國《明鏡周刊》喺兩星期前爆料，指皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）喺2009年夏天於美國拉斯維加斯強姦一名20歲女子蘇珊（化名），更令對方直腸受傷，最終以支付37.5萬美元（約292萬港元）掩口費了事。雖然C朗當時透過律師表示報道完全失實，純屬「傳媒創作嘅小說」，但《明鏡周刊》周四再度披露C朗喺2010年親筆簽署嘅庭外和解文件，顯示整份文件以「Topher」代表C朗，仲講明「有簽名有真相」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170428/large/1493351029_b8b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170428%2Flarge%2F1493351029_b8b9.jpg&h=5288f86c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fc211941a3bff1d86d6b1a28b2ee00a696daace","tid":913966,"uid":34571,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:32:34.000Z","msg":"點解沙高要停賽"},{"pid":"1bcd9dd4456d61df421268269aa4794b979f1401","tid":913966,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fc211941a3bff1d86d6b1a28b2ee00a696daace","tid":913966,"uid":34571,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:32:34.000Z","msg":"點解沙高要停賽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:38:08.000Z","msg":"足球嘢，金錢操控，利益輸送比較大，好多嘢左手交右手就了事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰維斯軒斯古積特被爆服禁藥<br />\n2017/08/23 01:04  <br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=oPV7m1N%2BLefFuRADm1MhdIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=9e986564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】一份疑因黑客入侵而洩漏的國際足協文件顯示，包括泰維斯、軒斯、古積特等球星在內的25名球員，都曾使用含禁藥成分的藥物，卻獲准許出戰2010年世界盃。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒報道，一個專門竊取星級運動員醫療紀錄的黑客組織，最近得到一份國際足協文件，上面列出25位國家隊球員使用含禁藥成分的藥物，但獲批准參與2010年南非世界盃決賽周。<br />\n<br />\n該份為數25人名單中，列出球員名字、所屬國家隊及使用藥物；當中有不少為球迷認識的名字，例如現在仍馳騁球場的阿根廷前鋒泰維斯（Carlos Tevez）及荷蘭籍攻擊球員古積特（Dirk Kuyt）。<br />\n<br />\n泰維斯、軒斯，以及另外3位阿根廷球星迪亞高米列圖、華朗與森美爾，都有使用名為Betamethasone的藥物。據悉Betamethasone為一種藥膏，主治皮膚問題，內含禁藥類固醇。此外，古積特則有使用Dexamethasone，也是一種治療皮膚疾病的含類固醇藥物。<br />\n<br />\n名單上的25人都有向國際反禁藥組織申報用藥情況，而且沒有被指控服用禁藥。"},{"pid":"d7a0d2b806292dd15f211298850f61604c25e858","tid":913966,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:47:54.000Z","msg":"又陰啲陰啲做鳩吾皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ddf91c78d18d1a62b6f3cfccbdeddd2263ac54","tid":913966,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:58:48.000Z","msg":"重賽啦"},{"pid":"013643719135821a5098023eafcfde8c9165a61b","tid":913966,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:27:55.000Z","msg":"阿根廷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fce68303885ccb60a82688cc5b0e80b42b2051","tid":913966,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:30:53.000Z","msg":"怨婦大軍準備"},{"pid":"4a3932fff7ffe74b7d91ee5d58d259a5c9161298","tid":913966,"uid":47783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27ddf91c78d18d1a62b6f3cfccbdeddd2263ac54","tid":913966,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T01:58:48.000Z","msg":"重賽啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"牙朗4連R聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80569d1c829331d99c3baec2829fcc3690141932","tid":913966,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怨婦"},{"pid":"0b37683d0a457ac24730944f19f1c7a7c4e181ef","tid":913966,"uid":63536,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:02:04.000Z","msg":"俾番冠軍猁算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358564e95038861f2e88636fa8eb42a87b71e433","tid":913966,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"唔怪得會腦震盪"},{"pid":"46f276d7349f437a7696e1645de5da4b3d4896f9","tid":913966,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1093a1342f1f158e1421e9f6b75735d24bd9e8c","tid":913966,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:22:45.000Z","msg":"如果唔係拉莫斯食禁藥 <br />\n我地利記會輸?"},{"pid":"5b3f10422b18b42f076c0cf799251981a1a2e78a","tid":913966,"uid":166126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"《明鏡周刊》拿出了美國醫師協會定下的地塞米松使用規則。<span style=\"color: red;\">此藥可以在比賽前使用，但需要隊醫在藥檢時上報。如果隊醫沒有上報而最後檢測出陽性，就被視為有使用禁藥的嫌疑。下一步強制措施包括開始調查，這就是拉莫斯面臨的問題。但在和尿樣在一起的表格里，比賽前七天所使用的藥物一欄卻沒有提到地塞米松。</span><br />\n<br />\n歐足聯的報告記錄，拉莫斯在奪冠頒獎典禮後立刻出現在藥檢站，花了兩個小時抽取血樣和尿樣，直至0點26分，隊醫A&mdash;&mdash;同時也是西班牙國家板球隊的隊醫，是位創傷學家&mdash;&mdash;陪伴他接受藥檢，他和拉莫斯一起簽了字。<br />\n<br />\n在發現地塞米鬆後，隊醫成了替罪羊。他給歐足聯的報告像一份檢討。消息很清楚：拉莫斯是無辜的，是我，隊醫搞砸了。<br />\n醫生寫道，由於拉莫斯的左膝和左肩患有&ldquo;慢性病&rdquo;，<span style=\"color: red;\">他在歐冠決賽前一天兩次給球員注射地塞米松。他在比賽后的興奮劑報告中記下了錯誤的藥物，這是因為贏得冠軍和&ldquo;藥檢時的特殊情況&rdquo;導致的&ldquo;興奮&rdquo;。具體說，就是西班牙前國王胡安-卡洛斯陛下和西班牙總理經過藥檢站祝賀了拉莫斯。</span><br />\n<br />\n在混亂中，他犯了一個錯誤，混淆了兩種在興奮劑檢測中符合相同標準的類似物質。這是一次&ldquo;人為失誤&rdquo;，A醫生寫道，&ldquo;因此可以理解。&rdquo; 他寫道，他從未打算&ldquo;違反任何反興奮劑條例&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n在歐足聯的反興奮劑部門，醫生的聲明顯然受到歡迎。他們諮詢了一位&ldquo;專家&rdquo;，他確認兩次靜脈注射1.2毫升地塞米松會產生相當於球員尿液樣本中發現的地塞米松濃度的粗略值。歐足聯注意到俱樂部的解釋。球員和醫生&ldquo;極有可能&rdquo;犯了&ldquo;行政錯誤&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，<span style=\"color: red;\">歐足聯結案。 &ldquo;將來，我們會要求您和您的隊醫保持最謹慎，&rdquo;信中總結道，&ldquo;在完成興奮劑控製表格時，更確切地說是藥物申報表。&rdquo;</span>"},{"pid":"1077d2291b09d1051d40dd75c2dcffeb6d3223db","tid":913966,"uid":26862,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"原來祖雲達斯=利物浦"},{"pid":"abe4da6e84ed627b2831947278f57bce02f2c177","tid":913966,"uid":19527,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"0b37683d0a457ac24730944f19f1c7a7c4e181ef","tid":913966,"uid":63536,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:02:04.000Z","msg":"俾番冠軍猁算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"睇下邊年決賽先啦傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沖出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c775cb76c1e19652817b1a2c02c068a5a20e0cb4","tid":913966,"uid":1823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T03:33:59.000Z","msg":"好多文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76738e4288b148d61bee53cab14b59cbba4fb8c","tid":913966,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:01:56.000Z","msg":"拉狗唔係用禁藥會夠快mark沙拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"91b762dc7a7